00:37:16.915 --> 00:37:18.833
[inhales sharply]
<i>You didn't kill your wife.</i>

523
00:37:18.834 --> 00:37:20.334
Yeah. that's right.

524
00:37:20.335 --> 00:37:22.629
Amy Brancato killed Melissa. yes.

525
00:37:23.630 --> 00:37:28.051
No. no. I know that you got Amy to confess
but not because you were guilty.

526
00:37:28.927 --> 00:37:29.928
Okay.

527
00:37:30.720 --> 00:37:33.765
So. who killed Melissa?

528
00:37:35.308 --> 00:37:36.309
<i>Crystal.</i>

529
00:37:38.937 --> 00:37:41.272
<i>No. Crystal was in an institution.</i>

530
00:37:41.273 --> 00:37:43.817
No. Crystal got a guard to let her out.

531
00:37:46.069 --> 00:37:47.112
I can prove it.

532
00:37:47.946 --> 00:37:49.321
And I've got Crystal.

533
00:37:49.322 --> 00:37:51.157
<i>Look. Crystal was pregnant with your child</i>

534
00:37:51.158 --> 00:37:53.159
<i>and she was watching you
play house with Melissa.</i>

535
00:37:53.160 --> 00:37:54.243
<i>and she just snapped.</i>

536
00:37:54.244 --> 00:37:56.663
Wait. wait. wait. [chuckles]

537
00:37:57.289 --> 00:37:58.706
What did you just say?

538
00:37:58.707 --> 00:38:00.916
Crystal was carrying my child?

539
00:38:00.917 --> 00:38:02.377
[Anna] <i>Yeah. your kid.</i>

540
00:38:02.961 --> 00:38:05.463
The one that she said
she gave up for adoption.

541
00:38:05.464 --> 00:38:07.799
I don't know what she told you.

542
00:38:09.092 --> 00:38:11.052
But Crystal had a son.

543
00:38:12.929 --> 00:38:16.558
<i>And he's out there somewhere
and you can probably find him.</i>

544
00:38:18.393 --> 00:38:22.189
<i>I'm gonna text you an address
of a public place and we'll talk.</i>

545
00:38:23.440 --> 00:38:25.484
Then you are gonna leave me alone.

546
00:38:27.277 --> 00:38:30.697
You hear me? You're gonna leave me
and my family alone.

547
00:38:32.240 --> 00:38:34.284
<i>We didn't do this to you.</i>

548
00:38:36.495 --> 00:38:38.830
Okay. Send the address.

549
00:38:55.847 --> 00:38:56.848
[chimes]

550
00:38:57.808 --> 00:38:59.810
[menacing music playing]

551
00:39:12.155 --> 00:39:14.157
[menacing music intensifies]

552
00:39:16.785 --> 00:39:19.620
Is that your big plan. huh?
Just turn me over to Max?

553
00:39:19.621 --> 00:39:20.996
You think that's gonna win you back?

554
00:39:20.997 --> 00:39:24.708
[Crystal] He wants you even more
than he wants me. you bitch!

555
00:39:24.709 --> 00:39:26.169
[Anna gasps. yelps]

556
00:39:27.462 --> 00:39:28.505
[Robert] Get going.

557
00:39:29.297 --> 00:39:31.090
What now. Crys? Huh?

558
00:39:31.091 --> 00:39:33.342
How many times I gotta
wipe your shit off of my boot?

559
00:39:33.343 --> 00:39:35.845
I have a plan! Put her in the hold.

560
00:39:35.846 --> 00:39:37.513
- [Anna] No. please.
- [Robert] Get down there.

561
00:39:37.514 --> 00:39:40.725
- Get her in here. You need to go.
- [Anna] Don't do this. We can talk.

562
00:39:41.601 --> 00:39:42.726
[Robert] Close it up. boy.

563
00:39:42.727 --> 00:39:45.647
[Robert. Crystal
shouting indistinctly. muffled]

564
00:39:51.278 --> 00:39:52.529
[Crystal] Get out of here!

565
00:39:54.448 --> 00:39:57.491
[Robert] What were you planning on doing
if we ain't showed up?

566
00:39:57.492 --> 00:39:59.703
What. you think you were gonna
bash her on the head?

567
00:40:02.873 --> 00:40:04.207
[Crystal] Just leave me alone.

568
00:40:14.926 --> 00:40:16.010
[phone beeps]

569
00:40:16.011 --> 00:40:18.013
[line ringing]

570
00:40:20.891 --> 00:40:22.017
Don't hurt my son.

571
00:40:23.643 --> 00:40:26.854
[Max] <i>Tom. Set yourself free.</i>

572
00:40:26.855 --> 00:40:27.856
[call ends]

573
00:40:29.649 --> 00:40:31.067
[phone chimes]

574
00:40:32.027 --> 00:40:34.029
[ominous music playing]

575
00:40:46.833 --> 00:40:48.001
[breathing heavily]

576
00:40:51.755 --> 00:40:52.839
[sniffs]

577
00:40:56.843 --> 00:40:59.054
[breathing heavily]

578
00:41:05.102 --> 00:41:06.185
[knocks on door]

579
00:41:06.186 --> 00:41:09.814
Hey! I just need some air.
I'm having trouble breathing down here.

580
00:41:09.815 --> 00:41:11.440
- Please?
- Ma'am? [gasps]

581
00:41:11.441 --> 00:41:14.069
Oh. fuck.

582
00:41:14.694 --> 00:41:16.446
[gasps. yelps]

583
00:41:18.031 --> 00:41:21.700
Look. whatever the Cadys have done
for you. it is not worth it.

584
00:41:21.701 --> 00:41:24.161
[gasping]

585
00:41:24.162 --> 00:41:27.081
You keep running your mouth like that
and watch what happens to you.

586
00:41:27.082 --> 00:41:28.415
- Luke...
- [Luke groaning]

587
00:41:28.416 --> 00:41:30.751
...you don't wanna spend
the rest of your life in prison. do you?

588
00:41:30.752 --> 00:41:34.256
It'll be much easier
if you just shut up. ma'am.

589
00:41:34.881 --> 00:41:38.093
Oh. my God. [panting]

590
00:41:43.557 --> 00:41:45.474
- Are you okay?
- [Luke groans]

591
00:41:45.475 --> 00:41:46.934
Yeah. Yeah. I'm good.

592
00:41:46.935 --> 00:41:49.604
I've seen that scar before.
In your baby photo.

593
00:41:50.981 --> 00:41:52.356
[scoffs]

594
00:41:52.357 --> 00:41:53.607
What?

595
00:41:53.608 --> 00:41:55.610
[chuckles. pants]

596
00:41:57.028 --> 00:41:58.655
Does Max know you're his son?

597
00:41:59.489 --> 00:42:00.990
- What?
- [Crystal] That's not true.

598
00:42:00.991 --> 00:42:03.033
- I'm Crystal's son. ma'am.
- That's right.

599
00:42:03.034 --> 00:42:04.410
You're a lying bitch.

600
00:42:04.411 --> 00:42:07.371
- Max Cady is your dad. Luke.
- [Robert] She's lying. Luke.

601
00:42:07.372 --> 00:42:08.706
[Crystal] You shut the fuck up. bitch.

602
00:42:08.707 --> 00:42:10.583
- [Robert] Talking nonsense. Goddamn it.
- Why would you say that?

603
00:42:10.584 --> 00:42:12.209
- Nonsense. I'm telling you.
- She's a lying little bitch.

604
00:42:12.210 --> 00:42:14.003
- But Max is my mama's brother?
- Yeah.

605
00:42:14.004 --> 00:42:16.547
- [Robert] Son. goddamn it.
- She's a lying. deceitful little bitch!

606
00:42:16.548 --> 00:42:17.465
Shut her up. Luke!

607
00:42:17.466 --> 00:42:19.258
Yeah. but what about my dad. Mama?

608
00:42:19.259 --> 00:42:21.927
Your dad is... [stutters]
...exactly who I said he was.

609
00:42:21.928 --> 00:42:24.221
- he's a zero. he left a long...
- She's lying.

610
00:42:24.222 --> 00:42:26.140
You can tell she's lying. right?
Look at her.

611
00:42:26.141 --> 00:42:28.559
Don't you let her talk to that.
she's saying lies to you!

612
00:42:28.560 --> 00:42:30.144
[Robert] It's like I told you. Crys.

613
00:42:30.145 --> 00:42:32.980
Sins of the daughter
visit the whole goddamn family!

614
00:42:32.981 --> 00:42:35.733
Hold on. you're working yourself up.
I can see it.

615
00:42:35.734 --> 00:42:37.485
You settle down. boy.
or you gonna get some crate time.

616
00:42:37.486 --> 00:42:40.529
Am I gonna get fucking crate time? Huh?
Fuck you and your fucking crate time.

617
00:42:40.530 --> 00:42:42.281
- Don't talk to your grandpa like that.
- Huh?

618
00:42:42.282 --> 00:42:44.241
Tell me. Mama.

619
00:42:44.242 --> 00:42:45.910
I love you.

620
00:42:45.911 --> 00:42:47.328
- Don't fucking...
- I would never hurt you.

621
00:42:47.329 --> 00:42:49.955
- [Luke] Don't fucking tell me that!
- No. I would never hurt you.

622
00:42:49.956 --> 00:42:52.625
- She's a stranger. I'm your mother.
- Tell me the truth.

623
00:42:52.626 --> 00:42:55.212
She can't tell you the truth. huh?
She's lying to herself.

624
00:42:56.004 --> 00:42:58.006
- Would you shut up?
- [gasps. grunts]

625
00:42:59.424 --> 00:43:00.634
- [exclaims]
- Oh. Ma.

626
00:43:01.176 --> 00:43:02.676
[Crystal] Shut up!

627
00:43:02.677 --> 00:43:04.637
[grunting]

628
00:43:04.638 --> 00:43:05.889
[grunts]

629
00:43:06.598 --> 00:43:08.141
[Luke] Fuck you. you fucker!

630
00:43:09.684 --> 00:43:12.144
I fucking hate you. I fucking hate you!

631
00:43:12.145 --> 00:43:14.688
- Fuck you. you fucker! [grunts]
- [Crystal] Oh. God. Stop it!

632
00:43:14.689 --> 00:43:16.482
- You're gonna kill him!
- Get the fuck off me!

633
00:43:16.483 --> 00:43:18.984
- You lied to me. you fuck!
- [Crystal] Stop it! [groans]

634
00:43:18.985 --> 00:43:21.446
- [Crystal] Don't!
- Why did you lie to me? What the fuck?

635
00:43:22.405 --> 00:43:24.908
[shouting indistinctly]

636
00:43:25.951 --> 00:43:31.081
Fuck you! Fuck you!
Why the fuck did you lie to me?

637
00:43:33.959 --> 00:43:35.459
[Crystal] Stop it. you're gonna kill him!

638
00:43:35.460 --> 00:43:36.711
[Luke] Get the fuck off of me!

639
00:43:39.673 --> 00:43:41.298
[Crystal] Luke. stop.
you're gonna kill him.

640
00:43:41.299 --> 00:43:43.759
- [breathing shakily]
- [Luke screams]

641
00:43:43.760 --> 00:43:46.262
- [Crystal] Calm down.
- [Luke] What the fuck am I doing here?

642
00:43:46.263 --> 00:43:49.766
I wanna fucking kill myself.
You're a bad mother!

643
00:43:50.392 --> 00:43:51.601
[Crystal] Calm down!

644
00:43:53.812 --> 00:43:55.814
[dramatic music playing]
